(12, 1, '2014-12-05 00:16:12', '2014-12-05 00:16:12', '2014 Season specific handouts.\r\n<h3>Regular Season Schedules</h3>\r\nLast updates:\r\n\r\nRookies: 5/9\r\nMinors: 4/14\r\nAAA: 4/27\r\nMajors: 4/14\r\nJuniors: 6/17\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2357077"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLRookies05-09-2014" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLRookies05-09-2014</a></span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2348951"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLMinorsRegularSeasonSchedule-4-14-14-01" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLMinorsRegularSeasonSchedule-4-14-14-01</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2352782"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLAAARegularSeasonSchedule-4-27-14-02" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLAAARegularSeasonSchedule-4-27-14-02</a>\r\n</span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2369227"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLJuniorsSchedule06-17-1" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLJuniorsSchedule06-17-1</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2348953"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLMajorsRegularSeasonSchedule-4-14-14-01" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLMajorsRegularSeasonSchedule-4-14-14-01</a></span>\r\n<h3>Registration, Parent Forms, &amp; Coaching Application</h3>\r\nThe 2014 Newsletter contains the registration form.\r\n\r\nAll players need to complete a Medical Release form for coaches to have on-hand during the season.\r\n\r\nParents can find details about the supplementary accident insurance provided by Little League International for all our players in the "LLI Insurance" handout below.\r\n\r\nProspective coaches need to fill out 3 forms: (1) Coaching application; (2) Coaches Code of Conduct; and (3) one of the Volunteer Background Check forms. If you coached for us last year, you can fill out the Returning form this year. Mail these forms back with your player''s registration or bring them to the *mandatory* Coaches Meeting on Feb. 26.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2326653"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014_VLL_Newsletter" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014_VLL_Newsletter</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2327307"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLCoachingApp" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLCoachingApp</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2327306"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014VLLCoachCodeofConduct" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014VLLCoachCodeofConduct</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2327304"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="Returning-VolunteerApp14" width="20" height="16" border="0" />Returning-VolunteerApp14</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2327305"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="VolunteerApp14" width="20" height="16" border="0" />VolunteerApp14</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2342077"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014Medical_Release_Form" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014Medical_Release_Form</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2342078"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014Es_Medical_Release_Form" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014Es_Medical_Release_Form</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2342079"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014WhatParentsShouldKnow" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014WhatParentsShouldKnow</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2342080"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014Es_whatparentsshouldknow" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014Es_whatparentsshouldknow</a></span>\r\n\r\nUmpires\r\nApplication, rules, etc. for umpires.\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2347720"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014_VLL_Rookies_Rules_2014-04-09" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014_VLL_Rookies_Rules_2014-04-09</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2347721"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014_VLL_Minors_Rules_2014-04-09" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014_VLL_Minors_Rules_2014-04-09</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2347723"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014_VLL_AAA_Rules_2014-04-09" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014_VLL_AAA_Rules_2014-04-09</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2347722"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014_VLL_Majors_Rules_2014-04-09" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014_VLL_Majors_Rules_2014-04-09</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2347724"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014_VLL_Juniors_Rules_2014-04-09" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014_VLL_Juniors_Rules_2014-04-09</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#1431538"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2008RulesQuestionsforUmpiresandCoaches" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2008RulesQuestionsforUmpiresandCoaches</a>\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/handouts/#2345397"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="2014UmpireApplication" width="20" height="16" border="0" />2014UmpireApplication</a></span>\r\n\r\nMore Handouts:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Coaches - Rules, drills, practice ideas, &amp; safety</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Handouts', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'handouts', '', '', '2014-12-05 04:02:00', '2014-12-05 04:02:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/AdvancedPHP/veronalittleleague/?page_id=12', 6, 'page', '', 0),
