(159, 4, '2014-12-05 01:41:53', '2014-12-05 01:41:53', '<span style="font-family: Arial;"><b>Monday, July 6</b></span>\r\n\r\n<a title="top" name="top"></a><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368786#complex">Verona Little League Complex</a></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368786#practice"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">Verona Practice Fields</span></strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368786#junior"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">Juniors Playing Locations</span></strong></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368786#dist4"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">District 4 Playing Locations</span></strong></a>\r\n<p align="center">  <img src="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/images/dividerblk.gif" alt="divider" width="600" border="0" /></p>\r\n<a title="complex" name="complex"></a><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;">Verona Little League Complex</span></strong>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-size: small;"><a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368786#top">top</a></span></div>\r\n<strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;">The Verona Little League Complex at Ceniti Park is located at:</span></span></strong>\r\n<p align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"> 601 E Verona Avenue. </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div><iframe src="http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&amp;msid=215889911072870926220.0004a5e11e51027f30d09&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=h&amp;ll=42.994133,-89.521708&amp;spn=0.015067,0.027466&amp;z=15&amp;output=embed" width="640" height="480" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div>\r\n<div>View <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?msa=0&amp;msid=215889911072870926220.0004a5e11e51027f30d09&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;t=h&amp;ll=42.994133,-89.521708&amp;spn=0.015067,0.027466&amp;z=15&amp;source=embed">Verona Little League</a> in a larger map</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div align="left"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;">From Beltline: Take exit 258 South. Go approximately 5 miles to Verona Rd/US-151/US-18 W exit 81 into Verona. Take a left at second stop light into VLL Complex parking lot.</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: large;">All league games are played at this location on one of the following fields:</span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: medium;">5th Quarter Field\r\nFrank-Homan Field\r\nLund Field\r\nHeartland Credit Union Field\r\n(the location of each field is indicated in the image below)</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p align="center"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: large;"> <img src="http://picasaweb.google.com/veronalittleleagueinc/WebsiteImages#5323766163668511346" alt="map" width="1" height="1" border="0" /><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/images/fields_aerial_w_name.gif" alt="aerial w/names" width="481" height="320" border="0" />\r\n</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: large;">\r\nVerona Little League will also play host to the Mid Summer Classic tournament in July 2011, please visit our <a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368796">2011 MSC tab</a> for more information.</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"> </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: x