(167, 4, '2014-12-05 01:51:07', '2014-12-05 01:51:07', '<span id="title"> 2014 Final Results </span>\r\n<div style="text-align: left;" align="center"><strong>10U Champs: Kennedy</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>4th seed: <strong>East-9</strong> d. East-10 (11-5)</div>\r\n<div>3rd seed: <strong>Verona-D</strong> d. Verona-ND (14-4)</div>\r\n<div>2nd seed: <strong>Reedsburg</strong> d. Kenosha National (7-2)</div>\r\n<div>1st seed: <strong>Kennedy</strong> d. Kenosha American (13-3)</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>11U Champs: DePere\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>4th seed: <strong>West</strong> d. Reedsburg (11-10 [7])</div>\r\n<div>3rd seed: <strong>Orangeville</strong> d. Kenosha National (9-8)</div>\r\n<div>2nd seed: <strong>Verona</strong> d. Kenosha American (11-8)</div>\r\n<div>1st seed: <strong>De Pere</strong> d. Kennedy (13-12 [7])</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>12U Champs: East</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>4th seed: <strong>Edgerton</strong> d. Verona (11-3)</div>\r\n<div>3rd seed: <strong>Kennedy</strong> d. Reedsburg (8-2)</div>\r\n<div>2nd seed: <strong>Janesville</strong> d. Kenosha National (9-6)</div>\r\n<div>1st seed: <strong>East</strong> v. Kenosha American (11-1)</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>13U Champs: Reedsburg</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>4th seed: <strong>Verona</strong> d. East (6-2)</div>\r\n<div>3rd seed: <strong>Fondy</strong> d. Sun Prairie (8-7)</div>\r\n<div>2nd seed: <strong>Middleton</strong> d. Renegades (8-7)</div>\r\n<div>1st seed: <strong>Reedsburg</strong> v. Kimberly (5-4)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a name="news3845974"></a><span id="title">VLL 2014 Mid-Summer Classic Tournament</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="Apple-style-span">July 4 - July 6, 2014</span>\r\n<div align="center">Questions/concerns - <a href="mailto:cneuroth@barneveld.k12.wi.us" rel="nofollow">cneuroth@barneveld.k12.wi.us</a></div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p align="left">Welcome to Ceniti Park, home of Verona Little League, for a weekend of great baseball! For directions to the complex, please visit the <a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368786" rel="nofollow">VLL &amp; Local League Info tab</a>.</p>\r\n<p align="left">Planning to stay overnight during the tournament? We have reserved blocks of rooms at nearby hotels. The following link contains details for lodging as well as a list of other local businesses to help make your stay enjoyable:</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/VeronaVisitorResource2013.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" />Verona Visitor Resources</a>\r\n<div align="left">Our Little League Complex includes a <a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368799" rel="nofollow">concession stand</a> with a large variety of food and beverage items. WiFi is also available on-site to help you stay connected without needing to leave the tournament.</div>\r\n<p align="left">Weather updates will appear through the Twitter link on our <a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/" rel="nofollow">home page</a>. You can follow <strong>@VeronaLL</strong> on Twitter to see these updates as soon as they are posted.</p>\r\n<iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m13!1m11!1m3!1d1355.5215860762232!2d-89.5195331727537!3d42.99263755550679!2m2!1f0!2f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1417741639285" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0"></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="title"> Complex Policies </span>\r\n\r\nFor the safety of all our visitors, we ask you to please respect the following VLL Complex policies:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>When there is lightning in the area, <strong>all games are put on an immediate 30 minute delay</strong>.  There are no exceptions to this rule.  Games will not resume until 30 minutes after the last lightning seen in the area.  Our League has very strict rules regarding this item.  <strong>The entire complex (including the covered concessions area and dugouts) must be evacuated for the entire time. </strong>We request that everyone gets into a hard top vehicle in the parking lot or leaves the area completely.</li>\r\n	<li>No alcohol.</li>\r\n	<li>No smoking.</li>\r\n	<li>No dogs.</li>\r\n	<li>No skateboards, rollerblades, or bike-riding on the concourse. We have a skatepark within walking distance of the park, just west of the Complex.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Umpires are to be treated with respect at all times. </strong>Umpire abuse will not be tolerated. Ejection from the game or team disqualification from the tournament may result. Managers are responsible for themselves, their coaches, players, and fans. More specific details about this expectation can be found in the tournament rules below.\r\n\r\nFinally, we ask you to <strong>please not carry in food and beverages</strong>. We have a fully stocked <a href="http://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/news/index.cfm?cat=368799">concession stand</a> that will be open during the entire tournament. Take advantage of the convenience so you don''t miss a pitch!\r\n\r\n<span id="title"> Tournament Rules &amp; Schedule </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" /><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/2014MSCRules-10U.pdf">10U Rules</a></li>\r\n	<li><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" /><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/2014MSCRules-11U.pdf">11U Rules</a></li>\r\n	<li><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" /><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/2014MSCRules-12U.pdf">12U Rules</a></li>\r\n	<li><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" /><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/2014MSCRules-13U.pdf">13U Rules</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/10Uschedule-2014.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" />10U Schedule</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/11Uschedule-2014.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" />11U Schedule</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/12Uschedule-2014.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" />12U Schedule</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="https://www.eteamz.com/VeronaLittleLeague/files/13Uschedule-2014.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.eteamz.com/z/admin/images/file_pdf.gif" alt="PDF File" width="20" height="16" border="0" />13U Schedule</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a name="news5200929"></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>We will attempt to keep these results accurate and up-to-date during the tournament weekend. However, the tournament records and officials at the Complex are the definitive authority for results and seedings. </strong>\r\n\r\nNotes:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Games are not necessarily listed in chronological order in these widgets (they are grouped into matchup "rounds"). Use the PDF schedules above for a straight timeline view. The PDF schedules are the master schedule, if there are differences/typos.</li>\r\n	<li>To view each pool''s standings in the Pool Play widgets, click the <strong>Pools</strong> link in the header of the standings widget. Then use the arrow in the upper right to switch between pools.</li>\r\n	<li>Tournament seeding rules: Record, Head-to-head, Runs allowed per inning played, Runs scored per inning played, Coin flip. Note that the <em>Points</em> column below is tracking total runs scored, not something we can control...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div id="etz_pp_widget_pv">\r\n<div id="pool_container_0">\r\n<div class="header_bar toolbarbackgroundcolor toolbartextcolor">\r\n<div id="tournament_title">2014 10U MSC Pool Play</div>\r\n<div id="panel_nav">Standings | <a>Pools</a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div id="panel_pool_nav" class="poolnavbackgroundcolor poolnavtextcolor poolnavborder poolnavborder_combined_standing">\r\n<div id="combined_standing_outer_header" class="pool_title">Combined Standings</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="standings_panel">\r\n<div id="panel_content_0" class="panel_content poolshowing toolbarbordercolor">\r\n<div id="pool_content_0">\r\n<div class="spacer_15"></div>\r\n<table id="box_combined_standing_header" class="table_style menubordercolor" border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr id="combined_standing_header" class="menubackgroundcolor menutextcolor">\r\n<td class="table_header_bar" width="20%">Competitors</td>\r\n<td class="table_header_bar" align="center" width="16%">Wins</td>\r\n<td class="table_header_bar" align="center" width="16%">Losses</td>\r\n<td class="table_header_bar" align="center" width="16%">Ties</td>\r\n<td class="table_header_bar" align="center" width="16%">Points</td>\r\n<td class="table_header_bar" align="center" width="16%">W/L/T%</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr id="combined_standing_team_0">\r\n<td class="table_row" title="Kennedy" align="center" valign="bottom"><span class="table_content">1.</span> <span class="table_content">Kennedy</span></td>\r\n<td class="table_row" align="center" valign="bottom"><span class="table_content">3</span></td>\r\n<td class="table_row" align="center" valign="bottom"><span class="table_content">0</span></td>\r\n<td class="table_row" align="center" valign="bottom"><span class="table_conte